    Inferno, and two of the clones converged on Starscream 
like...well....ants. Inferno fell to the ground with the fire, but two of the 
clones sent a solid stream of fire each at Star Scream, and when Inferno got 
himself together, pelted him with several fire balls.
    
    The clone of Megatron arrived on the scene. He looked at the battle, and 
in his zombie like state raised his pistol and let off a few blasts at the 
oncoming Kitkat. That was the main target, her or Phobia.
